title: All-Star Holidays 2015 Food Network Special PDTV.x264-JIVE
description:
All-Star Holidays 2015




We're cooking up some of our favorite holiday recipes from the kitchens of our Food Network family, as Giada De Laurentiis, Ree Drummond, Guy Fieri, Bobby Flay, Nancy Fuller, and Ina Garten share their best tips and secrets for whipping up holiday classics. Join them as they make delicious and irresistible holiday dishes, including oysters Rockefeller, Christmas ham, juicy prime rib, spiced cider and red velvet cupcakes.




Original Air Date: 09-Dec-2015
